    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249390/extras/3bfa123f8d0dcb655222f0ccebda4e4b.webp?t=1729541491\" width=384 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in ancient Egypt, this adventure game follows the pharaoh's son on a quest to find a powerful magic stone hidden by the gods. The stone's location is scattered across four scrolls, each guarded by mythical creatures in secret chambers. Players must solve puzzles, battle enemies, and piece together the scrolls to unlock the stone's power and save Egypt from its enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Featuring:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8bit style pixel art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret Passages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original Soundtrack &amp; SFX</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249390/extras/7fb7e9e78267f45c3a60be84548b3fad.avif?t=1729541491\" width=194 height=192 /></span></p>",
